                "Boch"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "After a study trip to Rome in 1857 and the fortuitous acquaintance of scholars at the DAI (deutsches Arch\u00e4ologisches Institut or German Archaeological Institute), Michaelis went to Greece with <a href=\"/conzea\">Alexander Conze</a>.": [
